# To-Do Nomenclature

## File Naming

`YY-MM-DD_short-description.md` (e.g. `26-02-15_mvp.md`)

## Status Markers

- `[x]` Finished
- `[ ]` Planned
- `[~]` Ongoing (in progress, partially done)

## Structure

Each to-do file should have:
1. A title with date
2. Grouped tasks by category
3. Status markers on each item
